# CODEOWNERS for smackypants/trueai-localai
#
# Every pull request that touches a path listed here requires an approving
# review from one of the listed owners before it can be merged. Combined with
# the "Require review from Code Owners" rule in the default-branch ruleset
# (.github/rulesets/protect-default-branch.json), this ensures that *every*
# change to the project must be approved by the project owner (or an
# explicitly authorized agent identity).
#
# To add another approved agent / bot identity, append its GitHub handle to
# the lines below. Bots that act through a GitHub App (e.g. Copilot's coding
# agent, Dependabot) cannot be CODEOWNERS themselves; instead, add them to the
# bypass list in the rulesets under .github/rulesets/.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                           @smackypants

# Extra-sensitive paths — keep ownership explicit even if the glob above
# changes in the future.
/.github/                   @smackypants
/.github/workflows/         @smackypants
/.github/CODEOWNERS         @smackypants
/.github/rulesets/          @smackypants
/LICENSE                    @smackypants
/NOTICE                     @smackypants
/CONTRIBUTING.md            @smackypants
/SECURITY.md                @smackypants
/package.json               @smackypants
/package-lock.json          @smackypants
/android/app/build.gradle   @smackypants

# Agent surface — every prompt, instruction file, sub-agent definition, tool
# registry, and runtime adapter that an LLM-driven agent reads or executes
# *must* be approved by the project owner. These paths control how Copilot
# and any external agents behave inside this repository, so unreviewed changes
# here have outsized blast radius (prompt injection, tool drift, data leaks).
#
# Keep this list in sync with the `risk:agent-surface` classifier in
# scripts/classify-pr-risk.mjs — both should match the same path set.
/AGENTS.md                                  @smackypants
/.github/copilot-instructions.md            @smackypants
/.github/copilot/                           @smackypants
/.github/agents/                            @smackypants
/src/lib/agent/                             @smackypants
/src/lib/llm-runtime/ai-sdk/                @smackypants
/scripts/classify-pr-risk.mjs               @smackypants
/scripts/check-prompts-lock.mjs             @smackypants
/scripts/check-instructions-drift.mjs       @smackypants
/scripts/check-agents.mjs                   @smackypants
